:D Nailed it! I would like to echo faulk_wolf&#39;s suggestion to put it all in one mod. With something like this it will only work if the user has ASET. Then if you or anyone ever re uses your internal it will catch those parts too. Thank you for the work you have done!!<br>
[code]<br>
@PART<br>
[*]:HAS[@INTERNAL[mig]]:NEEDS[ASET]<br>
{<br>
@INTERNAL<br>
{<br>
@name = migASET<br>
}<br>
MODULE<br>
{<br>
name = RasterPropMonitorComputer<br>
}<br>
}<br>
[/code]
